[src:javascript/api-http-p03] Sending a 'Content-Length' header will disable the default chunked encoding.
[src:javascript/api-http-p03] Sending an 'Expect' header will immediately send the request headers.
[src:javascript/api-http-p03] Usually, when sending 'Expect: 100-continue', both a timeout and a listener for the `'continue'` event should be set.
